Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:36.05,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,480)}模仿和无意识
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经和亚城木君谈过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是昨天的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为不去触碰它反而更好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让他们觉得编辑部并没有将此视作问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而更不能由我们来提起这个话题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被问起 我觉得只要一笑而过就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:03:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 不该让他们看到我们过激的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最需要细心留意的是作家的精神面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了这点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个不是会因为这点事而气馁的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所说的话就最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 原稿 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两话完结的情人节故事  收尾不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接着下次讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个服部先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是和以前一样 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个银行抢劫的事件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在「PCP」中已经提过会给保安公司和银行添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此不能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,编辑部甚至已经对一部分报道提出抗议了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以一切照常即可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像之前说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要作品中真他们所实行的完全犯罪有可行性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.99,0:04:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让孩子们想去模仿就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部先生说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「PCP」不是助长犯罪的漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是从主人公们的计划策略陷阱等中获得乐趣的漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然自连载开始就收到抗议的电话和信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但撇开这些 它已经成为了人气漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是读者理解我们的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这次的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经完全不可能动画化了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 「白色情人节大作战」的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把这个作为NAME吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城君 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部先生 还在公司里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木的原作文章写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一点我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很在意？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我传真给你 能不能看一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实这风格和之前有点不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 果然是受了那个事件的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 可能是因为我们目前一直担心那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会出现这种错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先观察段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他有意持续这风格我们再想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次轮到我的漫画动画化了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想要增加一个工作人员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.52,0:06:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要个高水准的工作人员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还有意复出的话 就到我这来工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福田君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能别再管我的事了么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:06:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.36,0:07:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么会这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 平丸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍树
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中井先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！中井？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍树 全都是因为你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}苍树 快给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优梨碳 我现在就赶过来 尽量争取些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍树
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我等到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中井！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你碰优梨碳一根手指的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平！丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平丸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍树
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 优梨碳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不能出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍树
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再缠着苍树小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是那个女人的错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这根本是恩将仇报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了很多传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扰乱了你漫画人生的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是因为你对漫画的执着不过如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍树小姐和她的美丽没有罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 我会拼上我的性命来守护她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在你满意之前揍我就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平丸先生 你完全没有被打的理由 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 优梨碳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是男人和男人之间的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打的话就打我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也应该是中井先生最希望的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 请揍我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揍到你满意为止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩将仇报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当初其实只剩下漫画了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经赌上人生的一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Hideout Door」连载的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了那个的现在的我已经一无所有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道那是我自己的错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也已经没有希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后我到底该怎么活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中井先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫画真是太恐怖了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被编辑骗进这个行业
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果最后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一失足就是无边的黑暗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年后十年后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我 到时候会变成什么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.42,0:10:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要到我那里做助手啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中井先生可能就是我的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到这个我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才听到你说拼上性命守护她的时候就在想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把苍树托付给这个男人应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点儿臭屁 但还是谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}貌似是为了争风吃醋打架
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}好像终于有同伴来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}到底是干什么来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像两个人都麻烦了警察一整晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后不知怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像成为平丸先生的助手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 中经先生到底在干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟吉田先生说下要好好监视他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这周的本报是第8位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！第8位？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前一直是5位以内的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白色情人节那话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木君你从那一话开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻意回避在「PCP」中加入犯罪元素了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是和往常一样在写故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你无意识中写出了避免招惹问题的内容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你自己没那么想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大脑却擅自行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近一个月来的原作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明显的改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这次会有意识地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写出让他们不去模仿的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把你指出的地方全部修改
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋~人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒有点反复
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以先来跟你说声晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们有了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子模仿「PCP」的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是会不高兴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会教给他们什么该模仿什么不该模仿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香耶你是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.47,0:12:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一直是第2位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保持住这个状态哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 原稿我就拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄二郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2位和第1位差多少票
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…应该有50票以上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50票啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:12:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从来没关心过问卷调查什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话的NAME可能会晚一些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚一些？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你往常都很快所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次和往常不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是要得到第1位的NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让我去东京我有一个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,条件？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我成为JACK最受欢迎的作家的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我结束一部我讨厌的漫画的权限
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得…得到第1位？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要得到第1位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城君 NAME还没完成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间上已经很紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚…刚才高木把文章原稿拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去你那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画NAME吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 高木君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很累的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要事先准备后两话的原作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还完全没有做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在家创作的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用讨论了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原案已经有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写好了之后会拿过来看的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是之前高木未采用的原作之一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个拿出来用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为是已经走投无路了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个明显没有之前的犀利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明情况的话应该能休息一周…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木也应该不想这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,延迟的部分我会填补的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「PCP」第12位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.85,0:15:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来从未出现过两位数排名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连续三周…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄二郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「CROW」好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这周和第1位差不到20票
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就要得第1位了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责的作品形势大好却那副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来你还不是一样 最近一脸阴沉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为「PCP」状态不理想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去喝杯咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束一部讨厌的作品的权限？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你太大声了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事只有我和编辑长两个人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要对任何人说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明之前从不在意问卷调查的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么突然认真起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且就算是第1位也不等于就是JACK最受欢迎的作家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道新妻君作为亚城木粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得现在的「PCP」没有读的价值而想让它完结？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这周的速报已经出了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「PCP」目前13位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 估计这周「CROW」是第1位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是速报 但它和第2位差距不小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高 你老实说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个故事能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不过是新瓶装老酒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是作为一个故事还是很有条理的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有时间了 这次就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人你觉得这样就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城君 日程已经很紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作画的时间也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木要干的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我熬夜个3天也没任何问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我这就回家去写
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要写出真城认同的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木君已经到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 即使快到期限
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木也一定会写出让人认可的原作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会画出最好的画稿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相使出全力协助对方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是亚城木梦叶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高信任我等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要做到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了最高 为了亚城木梦叶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次放置在金库中的信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与连载于周刊少年JACK上的漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「PCP完美犯罪党」中的主人公一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留有PCP的字样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方认为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.60,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs30\pos(692,166)\c&HFDFDFD&\3c&H3D3E40&}到此一游
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}这和前几日的金库入侵事件很可能是同一嫌疑人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部 好好支持亚城木君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木君怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他还没和我联系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的事件他就受了那么大的精神打击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能你们不原意 但也考虑考虑休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}至少这名犯人在看这部漫画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得写原作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}是啊 是啊 可以说是模仿犯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和真城说一下 今天休息比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我一个人待着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 …
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也把饭…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了让我一个人待着！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「PCP」目前第11位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 估计这周「CROW」是第1位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城打来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您拨打的用户暂时无法接听
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍后…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 消沉到连我的电话都不接了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 香耶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}可恶 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人现在的状况接不了电话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看到了新闻以后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就马上说要写原作 让他一个人待着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木第一次这么跟我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说要一个人待着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经什么忙都帮不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为那次盗窃事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要写上PCP这几个字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明PCP根本不会做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 PCP绝对不会做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 可恶 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是六塚君吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把从别人那里偷来的教科书藏在体育仓库
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 这样当然会让人发现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是PCP 绝对不会藏在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么时候发现犯人是我而不是PCP的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六塚君发出预告书
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.48,0:21:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果事件发生就会被人认为是PCP干的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你本来是打算模仿他们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我一开始就明白不是PCP所为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.48,0:21:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们不会偷别人的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不会给别人添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切照计划进行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功劳都转给明知了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我估计明知也能很快发现不是PCP干的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.09,0:21:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.18,0:21:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯法就沦为了罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.07,0:21:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪谁都会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.26,0:21:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们的手法可是别人学不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:22:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇~真超酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这周的「PCP」太过瘾了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子上升了3位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.21,0:22:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让模仿犯替罪真是明智的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还收到了很多表扬的粉丝信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「PCP」不是助长犯罪的漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让人明白这是什么漫画 我们该做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.33,0:22:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让模仿犯替罪 并创作否定其行为的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.14,0:22:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和高木都是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.79,0:22:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这组合还是一如既往的合拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.79,0:22:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这回尽给真城添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.96,0:22:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作画的日程很紧张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.73,0:22:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是亚城木梦叶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.57,0:22:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.68,0:22:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新妻君这周也是第１位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.16,0:22:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是英二 差距又拉大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 但是不管差距如何拉大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定要追上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.73,0:22:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:59.06,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}在不断奋斗的过程中最棒的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.43,0:23:03.60,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}让它成形的那一刻令倍加珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:08.23,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}好似战斗 又仿佛联手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.23,0:23:12.82,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}感觉（互相交织）  如此刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:17.41,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}所以更加努力奋斗吧 保持自己的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.41,0:23:22.50,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}（未来） 肯定就在这条延续下去的道路上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:27.54,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}信念各不相同的伙伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.54,0:23:32.09,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}Rival…and Friend！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:35.30,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}互相碰撞的Pride
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.30,0:23:43.60,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}无法让步 今后仍将继续贯彻自己的作法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:45.90,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}准备已经完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:50.36,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}一口气追上去所需的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.15,0:23:53.53,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}永不放弃的 Pride
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.78,0:24:01.91,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}拼尽全力 因为喜欢所以在心中培养这份好感
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.25,0:24:06.92,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}虽然不知道等待我们的会是怎样的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:09.84,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}（明天）我还是会（尽可能的）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.84,0:24:12.55,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.65,0:24:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新妻君说出了不得了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.96,0:24:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想做有损形象的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.23,0:24:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你也太极端了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.00,0:24:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 连续和阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.98,0:24:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了守护梦想必须贯彻自己的做法
